        OH_YOU_RE_BACK_I_WAS_AFRAID_WE                                        = 10934,  -- Oh, you're back! I was afraid we'd lost you to some foul creature prowling the wilderness. Let's start from the top, shall we?
        OH_WHAT_RE_YOU_DOING_HERE_AREN_T                                      = 10935,  -- Oh, what're you doing here? Aren't you in the middle of a run right now? Couldn't stand to be parted from your favorite smile sergeant, maybe? Teehee!
