        TRAVEL_TO_TRAVEL_USING_GIL_GIL_TRAVEL_USING                           = 12293,  -- Travel to %? [Add to favorites/Delete from favorites]. Travel using # gil. (# gil) Travel using # tab[/s]. (# total) One-time free Warp for the objective. Not just yet.
