        TRAVEL_TO_WHICH_REGION_ON_SECOND_THOUGHT_NONE                         = 12303,  -- Travel to which region? On second thought, none. Select from amongst favorites. [San d'Oria/Movalpolos]. [Bastok/Tavnazian Arch]. [Windurst/Lumoria]. [Jeuno/Mamool Ja Savage]. [Tavnazia/Halvung]. [West. Aht Urhgan/Arrapago Is]. [Adoulin Isles/Ruins of Alzadaal]. [Ronfaure/Ronfaure Front]. [Zulkheim/Norvallen Front]. [Norvallen/Gustaberg Front]. [Gustaberg/Derfland Front]. [Derfland/Sarutabaruta Front]. [Sarutabaruta/Aragoneu Front]. [Kolshushu/Fauregandi Front]. [Aragoneu/Valdeaunia Front]. [Fauregandi/East. Ulbuka]. [Valdeaunia/Ra'Kaznar]. [Qufim/]. [Li'Telor/]. [Kuzotz/]. [Vollbow/]. [Elshimo Low/]. [Elshimo Up/]. [Tu'Lia/]. Previous page. Next page.
