        YOUR_LIST_OF_FAVORITES_IS_FULL_YOU_MUST                               = 12306,  -- Your list of favorites is full. You must remove an existing entry to add new ones.
        REMOVE_WHICH_ENTRY_NONE_OF_THESE                                      = 12307,  -- Remove which entry? None of these. %. %. %. %. %. %. %. %. %.
        WELL_IF_THIS_ISN_T_THE_CAT_S                                          = 12308,  -- Well, if this isn't the cat's meow. There is something you wish to ask of me? Hoping to have me shed some light on a particular matter?
        THIS_IS_WHOLLY_UNEXPECTED                                             = 12309,  -- ...This is wholly unexpected.
        I_VE_SEEN_FUTURES_BOTH_BRIGHTER_AND_DARKER                            = 12310,  -- I've seen futures both brighter and darker, but in each at least there was a future.
        AH_BUT_THOSE_FEATHERED_WINGS_REPRESENT_A_NEW                          = 12311,  -- Ah, but those feathered wings represent a new hope. A possibility to ensure that what should come to be...does come to be.
        PERHAPS_IT_S_BEST_IF_WE_NOT_PAW                                       = 12312,  -- Perhaps it's best if we not paw around here, and consult Atomos instead. Ask his opinion.
        WHICH_MEANS_THAT_YOU_LL_HAVE_NEED_OF                                  = 12313,  -- Which means that you'll have need of this.
        THIS_SHOULD_PROVIDE_ENTRY_INTO_WHAT_WE_CALL                           = 12314,  -- This should provide entry into what we call the Walk of Echoes.
        THE_ENTRANCE_THERE_IS_THE_SAME_AS_THE                                 = 12315,  -- The entrance there is the same as the entrance here--a cavernous maw. Gaping expanse of space.
        YOU_HAVE_COME_SHOWN_YOUR_FACE_BEFORE_ME                               = 12316,  -- %, you have come. Shown your face before me.
        ALEXANDER_S_CRY_HAS_REACHED_MY_EARS                                   = 12317,  -- Alexander's cry has reached my ears.
        AH_I_HAVE_AWAITED_YOU_HOPED_FOR_THIS                                  = 12318,  -- Ah, I have awaited you. Hoped for this chance.
        UNFURLING_HERE_BEFORE_YOU_IS_THE_WALK_OF                              = 12319,  -- Unfurling here before you is the Walk of Echoes.
        IF_YOU_LOOK_ABOVE_YOU_WILL_SEE_THE                                    = 12320,  -- If you look above, you will see the prime avatar Atomos given physical form...
        OR_SO_YOU_WOULD_THINK_NO_THE_ENTIRE                                   = 12321,  -- Or so you would think. No, the entire Walk of Echoes itself is Atomos. Its body and soul.
        SOME_REFER_TO_HIM_AS_THE_DESTROYER_OF                                 = 12322,  -- Some refer to him as the destroyer of worlds, for he feeds on futures that shall not come to pass. Whose existence is forbidden.
        I_TRUST_YOU_REMEMBER_THAT_ATOMOS_CONSUMES_ALL                         = 12323,  -- I trust you remember that Atomos consumes all futures that are forbidden.
        AND_I_M_SURE_THE_ONE_QUESTION_THAT                                    = 12324,  -- And I'm sure the one question that must be pulling at your mind--bothering you to no end--is why Atomos is not feasting on your dark future as we speak.
        I_TOO_HAVE_PONDERED_THAT_VERY_QUESTION_AND                            = 12325,  -- I, too, have pondered that very question, and I will not play cat and mouse with you--that future is not a forbidden one.
        THERE_IS_NOTHING_THAT_I_CAN_DO_WHAT                                   = 12326,  -- There is nothing that I can do, what with Atomos so intricately connected to the laws of this world. So important to the way Vana'diel plays out.
        OH_THAT_S_NOT_WHY_YOU_RE_HERE                                         = 12327,  -- Oh? That's not why you're here?
        WHY_ARE_YOU_HERE_I_NEED_IROHA_TO                                      = 12328,  -- Why are you here? I need Iroha to be accepted. No real reason.
        COME_COME_WE_ALL_KNOW_THAT_S_A                                        = 12329,  -- Come, come. We all know that's a bald-faced lie. Nothing could be further from the truth.
        OUT_WITH_IT_YOU_LL_NEVER_GET_WHAT                                     = 12330,  -- Out with it. You'll never get what you wish for unless you ask.
        WHAT_A_PERPLEXING_CONUNDRUM                                           = 12331,  -- What a perplexing conundrum.
        I_AM_QUITE_LUCKY_TO_HAVE_BEEN_PROTECTED                               = 12332,  -- I am quite lucky to have been protected by the Goddess, but you...a great pair of white wings has wrapped you in its embrace, although I'm hard-pressed to say why. I haven't got a whit of an idea.
        BUT_THOSE_WITHOUT_SUCH_A_BOON_CANNOT_TRAVERSE                         = 12333,  -- But those without such a boon cannot traverse the boundaries of time.
        WHY_WOULD_YOU_THINK_THERE_WOULD_BE_A                                  = 12334,  -- Why would you think there would be a means to save her?
        YOU_SHOULD_COUNT_YOUR_BLESSINGS_THAT_PHOENIX_FELT                     = 12335,  -- You should count your blessings that Phoenix felt the need to save her at all. Most would have been left by the wayside.
        WHY_THAT_DOUR_LOOK_DON_T_TELL_ME                                      = 12336,  -- Why that dour look? Don't tell me you're going to come mewling some trite complaint.
        WELL_OF_COURSE_I_M_UPSET_ISN_T                                        = 12337,  -- Well? Of course I'm upset! Isn't there anything we can do? I...suppose not.
        AN_UNSURPRISING_RESPONSE_TO_BE_SURE                                   = 12338,  -- An unsurprising response, to be sure.
        OF_COURSE_YOU_RE_UPSET_IT_S_UNDERSTANDABLE                            = 12339,  -- Of course you're upset. It's understandable.
        FORGIVE_MY_STARKNESS_A_THOUSAND_APOLOGIES                             = 12340,  -- Forgive my starkness. A thousand apologies.
        BUT_DON_T_MISTAKE_MY_HONESTY_FOR_CALLOUSNESS                          = 12341,  -- But don't mistake my honesty for callousness. Your story has shook me to the bones. Sent a chill up my spine.
        I_M_STILL_LETTING_IT_SINK_IN_A                                        = 12342,  -- I'm still letting it sink in--a force so mighty it can charm even Siren, the very mistress of seduction.
        I_M_POSITIVELY_AT_THE_END_OF_MY                                       = 12343,  -- I'm positively at the end of my rope. My wits' end.
        BUT_THERE_S_STILL_ANOTHER_OPTION_SURELY_I                             = 12344,  -- ...But there's still another option. Surely I don't need to tell you who Altana is.
        NEVER_ONCE_HAVE_I_BEEN_ABLE_TO_SET                                    = 12345,  -- Never once have I been able to set eyes on her.
        BUT_YOU                                                               = 12346,  -- But you...
        A_DAY_MAY_YET_COME_WHEN_YOU_WILL                                      = 12347,  -- A day may yet come when you will be able to see her in person. Become the most intimate of acquaintances.
        BECAUSE_YOU_AND_YOURS_ARE_CHILDREN_OF_THE                             = 12348,  -- Because you and yours are children of the Goddess.
        AND_YOU_BEAR_A_BRIGHTER_FUTURE_ON_YOUR                                = 12349,  -- And you bear a brighter future on your wings.
